# Useful HTML and CSS Codes

## HTML Codes

### 1. Basic HTML Structure
```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Website</title>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Your content goes here -->
</body>
</html>


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <title>About Us - (blessed)thanks</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>(blessed)thanks</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="products.html">Products</a></li>
                <li><a href="about.html">About</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Welcome to (blessed)thanks, your go-to destination for stylish fashion. Our mission is to provide you with high-quality clothing and accessories that make you feel blessed and confident every day.</p>
            <p>Founded in 20XX, (blessed)thanks has been dedicated to offering the latest trends while maintaining a commitment to quality and sustainability.</p>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2023 (blessed)thanks - Fashion Store</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

/* Reset some default styles for better consistency */
body, h1, h2, p, ul, li, button {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
}

/* Style the header */
header {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

header h1 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; /* Choose your preferred font */
}

nav ul {
    list-style-type: none;
}

nav ul li {
    display: inline;
    margin-right: 20px;
}

nav a {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: bold;
}

/* Style the product listing */
.product-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: space-around;
    padding: 20px;
}

.product {
    width: 300px;
    border: 1px solid #ccc;
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
}

.product img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
}

.price {
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #f60;
    font-size: 18px;
    margin: 10px 0;
}

/* Style the "Add to Cart" button */
button {
    background-color: #f60;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
}

button:hover {
    background-color: #e05100;
}

/* Style the footer */
footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 10px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
}


